title: El Caracol de Jade
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Very basic outdoor cocina economic place, serving antojitas. Located just next to the church stairs, west of the square. Has a vegetarian section on the menu with tacos, burritos, tortas and more. Vegans ask for no cheese or sour cream.
